      "time_str": "00:32.360",
      "text": "王韵婵：让我们敲希望的钟啊",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 38.88,
      "time_str": "00:38.880",
      "text": "多少祈祷在心中",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 45.38,
